    topic: "Obstetrics & Gynaecology",
    subtopic: "Endometrial hyperplasia",
    stem: `A 49-year-old woman presents with heavy irregular periods every 2 to 3 months lasting 7-10 days for the past seven years. She undergoes a diagnostic dilation and curettage (D&C) in the premenstrual period. Which one of the following findings on histological examinations, if present, is the most likely cause of her problem?`,
