    topic: "Obstetrics & Gynaecology",
    subtopic: "Cervical cancer screening guidelines",
    stem: `An 18-year-old girl comes to see you at a medical centre. She just has become sexually active with her new boyfriend. She is concerned about her risk of cervical cancer and is keen to follow your advice. Which one of the following would be the most appropriate advice in this regard?`,
