    stem: `A 21-year-old woman, who underwent dilation and curettage for termination of an unwanted pregnancy four days ago, presents to the emergency department with fever and purulent vaginal discharge. Her pregnancy was the outcome of sex with a stranger while intoxicated at a party. Which one of the following organisms is most likely to be the cause of her problem?`,
